---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Leo Club of Baddegama" description="Learn about BG Leos, the Leo Club of Baddegama in Galle, Sri Lanka, and how it serves the community through leadership and service.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-about" style="margin-top: -76px; padding-top: 150px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, #0f0f1e 100%); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background: url('/images/hero-1.jpeg'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; opacity: 0.5; animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
    
    <div class="container py-5 text-center text-white position-relative" style="z-index: 2;">
      <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4" style="font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff350, #ffc107, #e0a800); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; line-height: 1.2;">
        About the Leo Club of Baddegama
      </h1>
      <p class="lead mb-0" style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.8;">
        Leadership, Experience, Opportunity
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <h3 class="card-title text-warning mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
              <p class="card-text fs-5">
                To serve our community hand to hand by initiating meaningful service projects, empowering young individuals through leadership opportunities, and fostering teamwork, responsibility, and social awareness while making a sustainable difference in society.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <h3 class="card-title text-warning mb-4">Our Vision</h3>
              <p class="card-text fs-5">
                To be a leading youth organization that inspires unity, leadership, and compassionate service, creating a positive and lasting impact in the community
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About the Club -->
  <section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
          <p class="lead mb-4">
            The Leo Club of Baddegama is a dynamic youth organization dedicated to community service, leadership development, and personal growth. Functioning under the guidance of Lions Clubs International, our club brings together passionate young individuals who are committed to making a meaningful difference in society.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            Since its establishment, the Leo Club of Baddegama has actively engaged in a wide range of service projects focusing on areas such as education, healthcare, environmental sustainability, and social welfare. From organizing awareness programs and community development initiatives to supporting those in need, we strive to serve with compassion, unity, and responsibility.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            Guided by our club motto, "Hand to Hand," we believe in working together, supporting one another, and uplifting our community through collective effort. This spirit of unity drives every project we undertake and every life we touch.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our club also provides a platform for young leaders to develop essential skills such as teamwork, communication, and project management. Through fellowship and collaboration, we nurture individuals to become responsible citizens and future leaders.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-0">
            Inspired by the Leo motto, "Leadership, Experience, Opportunity," we continue to grow stronger while creating a lasting impact in our community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>